Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020. Sunny- slight waves
Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020. Cloudy- overcast- calm water
Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020. Cloudy- windy- 6-10" waves
Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020. Sunny- 6-10" waves- start of algae blooms

Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020. Sunny- slight waves- evenings killed algae bloom- dark green floating slicks on windward side of lake
Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020. Sunny- slight waves
Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020. Partly cloudy- windy- 8-12" waves- water temp dropping
Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020. Stained water- partly cloudy- very windy. Waves at times 12-16".
Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020. Overcast/calm.

Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020. Partly cloudy- calm water- water temp is 38 degrees- 3/4 of the lake was ice covered this morning. Last reading of the year.
Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020. Stained water- ice went out April 16- waves slight.
Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020. Stained water- sunny- waves slight. Clearest water I have ever seen.
Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020. Stained water- sunny-waves slight.
Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020.
Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020. Stained water. Heavy rains all week.

Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020. Public perception due to stained water.

Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020. Stained water- some suspended and floating algae present in parts of lake.
Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020. Very high water- floating and suspended algae- possible lake turnover.

Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020. Water green from algae- brown from stain. Floating and suspended algae- thick layer on down wind side of lake.
Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020. Still suspended and floating algae- weeds starting to die off in certain spots

Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020. Stained water- very windy last 4 days- surface water temp. 50 degrees- sunny today- water clearing.

Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020. Stained water. Very windy last 2 days- sunny today.
Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020. Hot and humid- sunny with mild breeze.
Updated from station 643341 (Boot Lake WBIC 2756400) to station 643053 (Boot Lake WBIC 1619100). JCD March 2020. Water stained. Water level low.
